Articles.Content:
Hello. I got a new laptop and freshly installed KSP which did run without any issues on my old laptop but now it crashes every time I try to build something. As you can see there is no crash report or anything, it happens every time, I got like 2-3 minutes then it crashes 

v1.1.3.1289 (x64)

windows 10

Edited October 8, 2016 by jsisidore
typo

edit: I think I found the log, it was the only log file in the game's directory, I assume logs get overwritten every time I launch a new game.
